                                <h2 class="mt-6 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Add Sub units</h2>

                                <p class="mt-4 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                                    A subunit is referred to as the 'alias' of a truck. This allows assigning subunits to a truck. For instance, if a truck experiences technical issues and cannot continue its journey, it is temporarily replaced by another vehicle until it is repaired.

                                    All trucks can serve as subunits for each other.                                </p>
